<div id="dif-changes-modal" class="fixed inset-0 {{ showDifChangesModal ? '' : 'hidden' }}" style="z-index: 2147483000;">
    <div class="absolute inset-0 bg-black/70"></div>
    <div class="relative h-full w-full" style="z-index: 2147483001;">
        <div class="h-full w-full flex items-center justify-center p-4 md:p-8">
            <div class="w-[80vw] h-[88vh] max-w-[80vw] max-h-[88vh] rounded-xl border-4 border-slate-900 overflow-hidden" style="background-color: var(--color-lightBlue); box-shadow: 0 28px 70px rgba(0, 0, 0, 0.55);">
                <div class="h-full overflow-y-auto p-6 md:p-10">
                    <h2 class="text-3xl font-semibold mb-4">Welcome to the new Dataset Information Form (DIF)!</h2>
                    <br />
                    <br />
                    <div class="text-gray-700 space-y-4">
                        <p>
                            The Dataset Information Form (DIF) has been updated to provide a cleaner, more intuitive interface for submitting and managing your datasets.
                        </p>
                        <p>
                            New features include:
                        </p>
                        <ul class="dif-changes-list">
                            <li>Cleaner look and feel</li>
                            <li>Tabs on the side to navigate sections</li>
                            <li>New spatial extent map</li>
                        </ul>
                        <p>
                            Important notes:
                        </p>
                        <p>
                            A listing of datasets that you have created are now located on the new "My Dashboard" feature
                            which can be accessed via the link above on the top navigation bar. If you would like to work
                            on a previously saved DIF, please use the Dashboard to load the DIF.
                        </p>
                    </div>
                    <div class="mt-8 flex flex-row items-center justify-end gap-3">
                        <button type="button" id="dif-changes-ok" class="button button-regular button-form justify-center px-4 py-2 text-sm">
                            OK
                        </button>
                        <button type="button" id="dif-changes-ok-dont-show" class="button button-regular button-form justify-center px-4 py-2 text-sm whitespace-nowrap">
                            OK - don't show this again
                        </button>
                    </div>
                </div>
            </div>
        </div>
    </div>
</div>
